{
  "stem": "13141.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was the ballistic expert in [NON-ENGLISH]-- that was where that rocket unit was stationed, near the Baltic Sea in the north of Germany.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he must have smelled something that I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because many of the of-- the-- the crew, in the Seventh Army Interrogation Center, I would say maybe 60% was Jewish and 40% was Gentile, but they all spoke German fluently.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Some of them spoke it very well, but most of them fluently.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he gave me all kinds of speeches about the relativity of the moon to the earth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What is being fired and the gravity, the pull of the gravity of the moon.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my goodness.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean-- I-- at that time, I never had taken any physics.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't even know what the man was talking about.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I told my commanding officer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, he passed it onto higher sources.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And about four or five days later, he was taken away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was shipped to the United States and was working with Wilfred Brown and all these people there in-- in-- where was it?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Someplace in the south of the United States.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I had a chance to talk to him whenever we walked, the prisoners and I walked, with Dr.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Kurtz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he asked me one day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, you know, he said, I was a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I belonged to the party.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was convinced-- he didn't say Nazi.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said [NON-ENGLISH], yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nazi is the abbreviation for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "National Socialist.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he said, most things I thought were correct, what was being done.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A few things I thought were not so good, but I never opened my mouth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I must admit that.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
